        <iri>
          <value>https://cdm.ovh/rst/cons/cons#includesRollingStock</value>
          <inverseFunctional/>
          <irreflexive/>
          <annotations>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://cdm.ovh/rst/cons/cons#includesRollingStock</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>includes Rolling stock</lexicalForm>
                <datatype/>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
            <annotation>
              <subject>https://cdm.ovh/rst/cons/cons#includesRollingStock</subject>
              <property>http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment</property>
              <object>
                <lexicalForm>This property describes the composition of a Formation. A Formation may incude any rolling stock (i.e. vehicles or formations). Irreflexive property: a formation cannot include itself; in other words, it may only have proper parts. This property and its inverse are ancillary properties, to be derived from the nested, listed rolling stock. Consistency of consist representations is the responsibility of the user.</lexicalForm>
                <datatype/>
                <language>en</language>
              </object>
            </annotation>
          </annotations>
